Description: |
    This repository centralizes research outputs, analytical tools, and 
    resources exploring and evaluating the United States agricultural safety net programs
    Supported programs include:
      * Federal Crop Insurance Program (FCIP)
      * Noninsured Crop Disaster Assistance Program (NAP)
      * Price Loss Coverage (PLC)
      * Agricultural Risk Coverage (ARC)
      * Ad-hoc disaster assistance programs
    Users can run Monte Carlo experiments to evaluate program
    payments, subsidies, and election decisions under alternative
    policy scenarios.
